# Lukess Home — Core Rules

## Stack
- Next.js 16 (App Router), TypeScript strict, Supabase, Tailwind CSS v4, Framer Motion
- Deployment: Vercel (lukess-home.vercel.app) | DB: same Supabase as inventory system

## Architecture
- app/page.tsx → homepage (Server Component)
- app/producto/[id]/ → product detail
- app/wishlist/ → wishlist page
- app/mis-pedidos/ → order history (authenticated buyers)
- components/cart/ → CartDrawer, CartButton, CheckoutModal
- components/wishlist/ → WishlistButton, WishlistClient, WishlistIcon
- lib/context/ → CartContext, WishlistContext (global state)

## Code Rules
- TypeScript strict — never use `any`
- Server Components by default — `'use client'` only when needed
- Error handling: try/catch with toast.error() + console.error()
- All Supabase queries filter by is_active = true for public-facing pages

## Design System
- Colors: Negro (#333333) primary | Dorado (#c89b6e) accent | Gris (#4a4a4a) secondary
- Font: Inter (Google Fonts)
- Animations: Framer Motion, duration 0.3s-0.6s, easeOut
- NEVER break the premium masculine aesthetic
- WhatsApp button: bg-[#25d366] text-white always visible

